name: Space Of Possibilities.
description:
So grateful for this space & the opportunities that have been presented to me this year. Like beyond sales, tweets, etc...just mentally & emotionally this year's journey into starting digital art has been an incredible ride for me and helped with finding myself again as a person. Still a long way to go, but feeling optimistic. Wishing the best in health for everyone out there! Thank you. -Daniel Jerome
